          can be a challenge. That’s why our Discord exists. It isn’t just a 
          chat server, it’s the official digital watering hole for the format.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you’re a thousand miles from the nearest LGS or looking for 
          a home for your local paper group, you belong here.
        </p>
        
        <a href="https://discord.com/invite/jq9KWHAdTm" class="discord-logo-btn">
            <svg 
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
              viewBox="0 0 127.14 96.36" 
              class="discord-svg"
              aria-label="Join the Official Discord Server">
              <path fill="#ffffff" d="M107.7,8.07A105.15,105.15,0,0,0,81.47,0a72.06,72.06,0,0,0-3.36,6.83A97.68,97.68,0,0,0,49,6.83,72.37,72.37,0,0,0,45.64,0,105.09,105.09,0,0,0,19.39,8.09C2.79,32.65-1.71,56.6.54,80.21h0A105.73,105.73,0,0,0,32.71,96.36,77.11,77.11,0,0,0,39.6,85.25a68.42,68.42,0,0,1-10.85-5.18c.91-.66,1.8-1.34,2.66-2a75.57,75.57,0,0,0,64.32,0c.87.71,1.76,1.39,2.66,2a68.68,68.68,0,0,1-10.87,5.19,77,77,0,0,0,6.89,11.1A105.89,105.89,0,0,0,126.6,80.22c1.24-23.37-3.55-47.54-19.9-72.05ZM42.45,65.69C36.18,65.69,31,60,31,53s5-12.74,11.43-12.74S54,46,53.89,53,48.84,65.69,42.45,65.69Zm42.24,0C78.41,65.69,73.25,60,73.25,53s5-12.74,11.44-12.74S96.23,46,96.12,53,91.08,65.69,84.69,65.69Z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Join the Community</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-media">
        <div class="video-container">
            <iframe 
                width="560" 
                height="315" 
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FnjumU1vRrk?si=rEG-zu43VlhiFT1i" 
                title="YouTube video player" 
                frameborder="0" 
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 
                allowfullscreen>
            </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </header>

  <hr />

  <section id="play">
    <h2>Where the Games Happen</h2>
    <article class="feature">
      <h3>The Official TLR Little League</h3>
      <p>
        Our year-long, free-to-play league. Every month is a new 
        chance to find glory (and sometimes prizes!).
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature">
      <h3>Weekly Tournaments</h3>
      <p>Regular events for those looking for a quicker competitive fix.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="feature">
      <h3>Digital & Paper</h3>
      <p>
        Most of our members play via Cockatrice, but you might find 
        a few ready for Spelltable (paper over webcam) sessions.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section id="brewery">
    <h2>Brew, Refine, Conquer, or just Yap</h2>
    <p>
      From "unplayable" jank to high-level optimization, we have 
      dedicated spaces for every mindset:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong><code>#Tavern:</code></strong> General chat and format talk.</li>
      <li><strong><code>#Brewery:</code></strong> Exploring new deck ideas.</li>
      <li><strong><code>#Competitive-Cellar:</code></strong> Optimization and meta-talk.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <small>
        Note: Don’t see a forum for your favorite Leader? Head to 
        <strong><code>#forum-requests</code></strong> and we’ll open one up for you.
      </small>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="governance">
    <h2>Stay Informed</h2>
    <p>
      The Committee lives here. Discord is the first place to see:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Ban & Watchlist Announcements</li>
      <li>Direct Rules & Committee Updates</li>
      <li>The <code>#Suggestions</code> Channel (Your voice matters!)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <aside class="next-step">
    <h2>Ready to Test Your Mettle?</h2>
    <p>
      One of the best ways to experience the format is through the  
      Official Little League.
    </p>
    <a href="/community/little-league">Learn more about the Little League &rarr;</a>
  </aside>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
  .community-hero {
    margin: 0 auto 5rem auto; 
    max-width: 1200px; 
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; 
    grid-template-rows: auto auto; /* Row 1: Title, Row 2: Content */
    gap: 1rem 4rem; 
    text-align: left;
  }

  /* Title Position (Row 1, Col 1) */
  .hero-grid h1 {
    grid-column: 1 / 2;
    grid-row: 1;
    font-size: 3.5rem; 
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem; 
    color: var(--heading-color);
  }

  /* Text Position (Row 2, Col 1) */
  .hero-text-content {
    grid-column: 1 / 2;
    grid-row: 2;
  }

  .hero-text-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Decorative Line (Row 1, Col 2) */
  .hero-line {
    grid-column: 2 / 3; 
    grid-row: 1;        
    
    height: 1px; 
    background-color: var(--border-subtle); 
    
    /* Pull left to bridge gap to text */
    width: calc(100% + 8rem); 
    margin-left: -8rem; 
    
    z-index: -1; 
    position: relative; 
    align-self: center; 
    margin-top: 2rem; 
  }

  /* Video Wrapper (Row 2, Col 2) */
  .hero-media {
    grid-column: 2 / 3;
    grid-row: 2; 
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 2rem; /* Vertical offset */
  }

  /* Video Embed Container */
  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 Aspect Ratio */
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    background-color: #000;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .video-container iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  /* --- DISCORD BUTTON --- */
  .discord-logo-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background-color: #5865F2;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem; 
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: transform 0.2s, background-color 0.2s;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.4);
    
    white-space: nowrap; 
    width: fit-content; 
  }
  
  .discord-svg {
    width: 28px; 
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    flex-shrink: 0; 
  }

  .discord-logo-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background-color: #4752C4;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.6);
  }
  
  .discord-logo-btn span {
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* --- MOBILE RESPONSIVE --- */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
        grid-template-rows: auto; 
        gap: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-line {
        display: none;
    }
    
    /* Reset grid placements */
    .hero-grid h1, 
    .hero-text-content, 
    .hero-media {
        grid-column: auto;
        grid-row: auto;
    }

    .hero-grid h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-media {
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    
    .discord-logo-btn {
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }
  }

  /* --- SECTIONS & FEATURES --- */
  #play {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column; 
    gap: 1.5rem;            
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .feature {
    background-color: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  ul li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem; 
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  code {
    background-color: var(--surface);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  /* --- NEXT STEP --- */
  .next-step {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .next-step h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .next-step a {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
</style>